            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#nehrichW" start="1371.509" end="x">Food we didn't get. There were guards every few meters, five, six meters there was an <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> man, and on the guns stuck bayonets. And we walked, in a few, few hours others fell, because of the frost and the cold and so on. We didn't have anything to drink, and they didn't give us any food. They simply evacuated us. They wanted to see who would last, and those who won't hold out, will hold out, who will not, doesn't have luck on his side.</span>
        </li>
