        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3545.394" end="x">Yes, but [unintelligible word]. Read a little with the melody, yes?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Wolf Nehrich</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#nehrichW" start="3556.060" end="x">Sorry?</span>
