                <span class="">Wolf Nehrich</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#nehrichW" start="3730.136" end="x">Yes. Political and additionally on top a yellow. That was [unintelligible word].</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3732.847" end="x">Ah, above were yellow signs. Now tell me this: Eh, how, Eh,eh: What are you planning to do now?</span>
        </li>
