            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Wolf Nehrich</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#nehrichW" start="3835.067" end="x">By heart. However you could.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3836.645" end="x">I see. And, eh, did many know the Jewish prayers by heart? Did you know some?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Wolf Nehrich</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#nehrichW" start="3843.362" end="x">[speaks over Boder] Those who knew, knew. Not everybody, not always did you pray. Sometimes, you recited the [unintelligible word] by heart, or sometimes the [unintelligible word, both probably Jewish prayers] and that was already something.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3852.940" end="x">I see. And why did you say, that eh things, eh, ok, Well, eh, so now you're planning to go to Palestine?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Wolf Nehrich</span>:
            </span>
