            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3892.203" end="x">[In English] This concludes the interview with Wolf Nehrich, eh, in <a class="placename" href="#vothL117">Geneva</a>, at, eh, August the 26th 1946. We curtail, that we finish that at, eh, the spool of 25 minutes. He has spoken one full spool and 25 minutes on the other. And that is about all. Eh, Illinois Institute of Technology recording.</span>
